{"tid":737174,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人越無知係咪會越開心","createTime":"2018-07-10T18:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T01:28:27.000Z","uid":151521,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a0e87b7fbb29085b66b1a78085a5dfc6f0e5edcd","tid":737174,"uid":151521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T18:52:29.000Z","msg":"話就話人有好奇心係件好事<br />\n但係好奇心往往累死人<br />\n好多事當你知道得越多就越會亂諗嘢<br />\n最後搞到自己好唔開心<br />\n<br />\n其實我人生已經夠唔開心<br />\n唔需要你來打沉我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd9316dbab1480c812e59ac767b3e7b624e8b0b","tid":737174,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T19:15:56.000Z","msg":"無知緊係好啦<br />\n就好似上幾代人無上網又無知 無比較好易滿足<br />\n假如你有能力睇到其他平行世界既自己<br />\n你都覺得灰嫁 依個自己係廢物黎<br />\n<br />\n不過你好似係煩緊愛情<br />\n當我9up"},{"pid":"1ebe973c5d7b5d1ec4142f9dda962cba8d4045ee","tid":737174,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T19:25:38.000Z","msg":"其實係責任<br />\n當知道同認識愈多野個陣<br />\n會背負愈黎愈多責任<br />\n責任限制左行為<br />\n令到人冇咁開心"},{"pid":"de1552edf16cb4f573091a653d4a167db2009e37","tid":737174,"uid":172390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T22:09:04.000Z","msg":"佢身邊嘅人會好撚唔開心"},{"pid":"2969d2f2a926bb4f52d2b45cf9a5c72a3939150c","tid":737174,"uid":19062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T01:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都算係<br />\n知太多野就好多野要諗過度過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}